3DViewFlip is sample project on animation,

I am performing animation on TextView. Animation include Rotation and Scaling  of TextView such that 
it looks like 3D animation.

I go the help from http://www.inter-fuser.com/2009/08/android-animations-3d-flip.html
which include rotation only so I have expanded the code and included the scaling and rotation together.

wish that help to someone
